        We are particularly interested in applicants holding at least a
        Masters diploma with some background covering one or several
        topics among large-scale data processing, unsupervised /
        semi-supervised machine learning, text mining and natural
        language processing (NLP). Due to the near deadline of this
        proposal, candidates from foreign countries should already have
        a work permit covering the internship period.</span></p>
